    <string name="info100">
        1)  Way of Use
        \n\n1.1)  This application is a  driven by voice \"todo list\" allowing to create new text events from your voice and if wanted synchronise them with your favorite calendar app (see Menu).
        \n\n1.2)  To use, you select a date = or > to the current date, you choose a time and you can record your event.
        \n\n2) Screen SELECTION OF A DATE.
        \n\n2.1)  current date without event  : dark blue
        \n\n2.2)  current date with event  : red
        \n\n2.3)  date with event > current date  : light blue
        \n\n2.4)  date with event \u003C current date : yellow
        \n\n2.5)  click on date with event : displaying screen SELECTION OF AN EVENT for the date.
        \n\n2.6)  click on date without event = ou > current date : you start a new event recording session.
        \n\n3) Screen SELECTION OF AN EVENT.
        \n\n3.1)  You may click an event to display screen DETAILS OF AN EVENT.
        \n\n3.2)  list of a date = or >  current date : You may record a new event for the date.
        \n\n4) Screen DETAILS OF AN EVENT.
        \n\n4.1)  You may modify the date AND the time AND the text of the event.
        \n\n4.2)  You may suppress the event.
        \n\n4.3)  the date and time passed events are in yellow.
        \n\n5) Menu.
        \n\n5.1)  You may delete all the events \u003C to a selected date.
        \n\n5.2)  on screen DETAILS OF AN EVENT You may suppress the event.
        \n\n5.3)  You may synchronised your new created event with your favorite calendar app.
    </string>
